node.text:
My two personalities waiting for an uber
.
.
I recently had a story poll about what toad you would like to see in plushie form and it was an insanely close race so I have two different samples (not pictured) in production right nowww. I can’t wait to share them on here when they’re ready. In the meantime, there will be a shop update of original illustrations that I’m ready to part with coming next week. Bye 🥿
